    "text": "On the morning of 14.07.2026, officers from the Thambuttegama Police Station conducted a raid in the Kudabibiliwewa area of the Thambuttegama Police Division and arrested two suspects who were allegedly carrying out an illegal excavation inside a house in search of antiquities. Excavation equipment believed to have been used in the offence was also seized.",
