    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      509.8,
      361.78,
      525.34
    ],
    "text": "Body Recovered \u2013 Galewela Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      539.92,
      511.09,
      603.73
    ],
    "text": "The Galewela Police have initiated an investigation following information received on the evening of 14.07.2026 regarding the discovery of the body of an elderly woman near Halmillagama Peelipalama in the Wayamba Ala area of the Galewela Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      618.31,
      480.27,
      649.93
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as an 82-year-old resident of the Galewela area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      664.51,
      515.85,
      712.21
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the woman had been suffering from a mental illness and had left her residence on the night of 13.07.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      726.79,
      512.62,
      774.51
    ],
    "text": "The body has been placed at the Dambulla Hospital mortuary for a post-mortem examination. Further investigations are being conducted by the Galewela Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
